code: /**  * Returns a live reference to the list of secure socket protocol names.  *  * @return a reference to the list, never {@code null}  */ public List<String> getSecureSocketProtocol() {     if (this.secureSocketProtocol == null) {         this.secureSocketProtocol = new ArrayList<>().     }     return this.secureSocketProtocol. }
